         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>[Manual process for direct dropship will be followed as called out in Subcontracting E2E-100 &amp; 48]
</text>
